      :ARG1-of (s / station-01 
            :ARG2 (c3 / country 
                  :name (n3 / name 
                        :op1 "Latvia")) 
            :op-of (w / within 
                  :mod (m / most))) 
      :op1 (a2 / and 
            :op1 (s2 / strength 
                  :mod (m2 / military) 
                  :mod (o / original)) 
            :op2 (c2 / country 
                  :name (n2 / name 
                        :op1 "Lithuania")) 
            :op3 (c / country 
                  :name (n / name 
                        :op1 "Estonia"))))

      :ARG0 (f / former) 
      :ARG1 (c2 / cluster 
            :mod (t2 / troop)) 
      :ARG2 (o / ownership 
            :mod (c / country 
                  :name (n / name

      :time (a / after 
            :op1 (d / disintegrate-01

                              :op1 "Union" 
                              :op2 "Soviet")))))
